WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.900 --> 00:00:09.000
Tongtong is my fault

2
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:10.766
I'm causing you trouble again.

3
00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:12.133
It's not your fault.

4
00:00:12.133 --> 00:00:13.366
What are you apologizing for?

5
00:00:13.766 --> 00:00:16.866
I know you didn't really want to drive me away just now

6
00:00:16.900 --> 00:00:18.966
Do you think there is an outsider like me?

7
00:00:19.133 --> 00:00:23.033
Brother Xiaoyu can't say some things normally, right?

8
00:00:23.300 --> 00:00:25.166
I really don't want you to go

9
00:00:26.733 --> 00:00:28.800
But I've been arguing with him recently.

10
00:00:28.866 --> 00:00:30.766
Oh, I know Tongtong.

11
00:00:31.066 --> 00:00:33.000
Do you think there are outsiders?

12
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.866
You and Xiaoyu don't have time to make out

13
00:00:38.066 --> 00:00:41.200
If I leave now, I'll be on fire

14
00:00:41.866 --> 00:00:43.000
Forget it.

15
00:00:43.966 --> 00:00:46.566
Hey, he's been very cold to me lately.

16
00:00:46.566 --> 00:00:48.033
inexplicable

17
00:00:48.333 --> 00:00:51.866
When was the last time you did that?

18
00:00:52.100 --> 00:00:55.500
We haven't talked since the last fight

19
00:00:55.500 --> 00:00:57.533
Well, you should make the most of your weekend

20
00:00:57.533 --> 00:00:58.600
You say

21
00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:02.466
Yueyue, please help me

22
00:01:02.666 --> 00:01:04.666
Well, that's not easy.

23
00:01:04.666 --> 00:01:08.166
You two go to the hotel for a weekend to spend time alone

24
00:01:08.266 --> 00:01:09.533
Enhance the relationship

25
00:01:09.533 --> 00:01:10.833
I'll book you a hotel

26
00:01:11.300 --> 00:01:13.400
Will it work? Trust me.

27
00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:15.966
I will definitely give you an unforgettable weekend.

